info.author: Olemis Lang
info.description:
Free Library of Object Oriented Programming Structures for Python (pyOOP)
	
	This package incorporates Object Oriented Programming structures 
	with no native support in Python.
	
	Included features are:
		oopdbc		Programming by Contract
	
	Relevant support features are:
		testing		Testing tools. Includes:
						- An object-oriented API to load and run doctests with unittest
						- Warning support for unittest test cases (and doctest)
info.name: pyOOP
info.summary: Free Library of Object Oriented Programming Structures for Python (pyOOP)
